public sealed class AppEvent extends EventObject permits AboutEvent, AppForegroundEvent, AppHiddenEvent, AppReopenedEvent, FilesEvent, OpenURIEvent, PreferencesEvent, QuitEvent, ScreenSleepEvent, SystemSleepEvent, UserSessionEvent
AppEvents are sent to listeners and handlers installed on the Desktop instance of the current desktop context.
